DESC="Rudiments is a C++ library providing base classes for things such as daemons, clients and servers, and wrapper classes.
Rudiments is an Open Source C++ class library providing base classes for
things such as daemons, clients and servers, and wrapper classes for the
standard C functions for things like regular expressions, semaphores and
signal handling.
"
